WEBVTT

00:09.843 --> 00:11.145
- ONE, TWO, THREE, FOUR!

00:11.179 --> 00:12.713
ONE, TWO, THREE, FOUR,
FIVE, SIX!

00:12.746 --> 00:13.747
TAKE IT, DUDE!

00:23.691 --> 00:32.066
*

00:32.100 --> 00:33.467
ONE, TWO, THREE, FOUR!

00:46.347 --> 00:47.815
[door buzzer]

00:53.587 --> 00:55.423
[knocks]

00:55.456 --> 00:56.557
- BRIAN!

00:56.590 --> 00:58.492
BRIAN!

00:58.526 --> 01:00.728
[knocking on door]

01:00.761 --> 01:02.630
BRIAN!

01:04.365 --> 01:05.699
[screams]

01:05.733 --> 01:10.504
[panting]

01:10.538 --> 01:13.174
- JUSTIN?
SWEETHEART...

01:13.207 --> 01:15.309
IT'S JUST A DREAM.
- MOM, DON'T...

01:15.343 --> 01:17.778
[whispers]
TOUCH ME.

01:17.811 --> 01:23.317
[sobbing softly]

01:23.351 --> 01:24.418
[sniffles]

01:24.452 --> 01:27.421
[upbeat music]

01:27.455 --> 01:35.396
*

01:49.243 --> 01:50.578
- MMM.

01:50.611 --> 01:53.481
GOD, I WANT HIS ASS.

01:53.514 --> 01:55.149
- WHO DOESN'T?

01:55.183 --> 01:57.618
- NO, NO I MEAN,
I REALLY WANT HIS ASS,

01:57.651 --> 02:00.354
INSTEAD OF THIS
TIRED OLD THING.

02:00.388 --> 02:02.656
- YOU'VE ALWAYS SAID YOUR ASS
IS YOUR FINEST FEATURE.

02:02.690 --> 02:05.693
- ONLY LATELY, IT'S LOOKING
A LITTLE...PEAKED.

02:05.726 --> 02:08.296
- YEAH, WELL,
MAYBE IT NEEDS A REST.

02:08.329 --> 02:10.331
- WHAT IT NEEDS...
IS A LIFT.

02:10.364 --> 02:12.433
- YOU'RE TOO YOUNG
FOR PLASTIC SURGERY.

02:12.466 --> 02:15.336
- HEH HEH, THIS LIFE
CAN WEAR YOU OUT

02:15.369 --> 02:17.771
BY THE TIME YOU'RE 30.
RIGHT, BRIAN?

02:17.805 --> 02:19.707
- [chuckles]

02:19.740 --> 02:21.509
- BESIDES, SELF-IMPROVEMENT

02:21.542 --> 02:23.311
IS SOMETHING WE SHOULD ALL
STRIVE FOR,

02:23.344 --> 02:24.778
NOW MATTER WHAT AGE.

02:24.812 --> 02:26.780
- TRUST ME,
TAKE IT FROM ME--

02:26.814 --> 02:29.883
GLUTEAL ENHANCEMENT
IS VERY PRICEY.

02:29.917 --> 02:31.652
- MY GOD, TEDDY!

02:31.685 --> 02:33.454
DON'T TELL ME
YOU'VE HAD WORK DONE.

02:33.487 --> 02:35.256
- YEAH, BECAUSE IF YOU HAVE,
I'D SUE.

02:35.289 --> 02:37.958
- HEH HEH. I'M SPEAKING
IN MY PROFESSIONAL CAPACITY

02:37.991 --> 02:40.261
AS A FINANCIAL ADVISOR.

02:40.294 --> 02:41.662
BUTT WORK COSTS BIG BUCKS.

02:41.695 --> 02:43.764
- BIG BUCKS, I DON'T HAVE.

02:43.797 --> 02:46.367
- WELL, MAYBE YOU COULD
SELL THAT OLD TIRED ASS

02:46.400 --> 02:47.401
FOR A NEW ONE.

02:47.435 --> 02:48.802
- [sarcastic chuckle]

02:48.836 --> 02:50.438
- I JUST GOT

02:50.471 --> 02:53.641
THE MOST FUCKING AMAZING
BLOW JOB.

02:53.674 --> 02:54.808
WANT A BUMP?

02:54.842 --> 02:56.810
- NO...THANK YOU.
LOOKS LIKE FUN, THOUGH.

02:56.844 --> 02:58.246
- WHAT'S WRONG
WITH YOU GUYS?

02:58.279 --> 02:59.913
- IT'S LATE.

02:59.947 --> 03:01.715
TOMORROW'S A WORKDAY.

03:01.749 --> 03:02.850
- YEAH, FOR SOME OF US.

03:02.883 --> 03:04.318
- SIGHTSEEING'S OVER.

03:04.352 --> 03:06.220
- IT'S EARLY, COME ON!

03:06.254 --> 03:08.522
WE JUST GOT HERE.

03:08.556 --> 03:09.890
LET'S PARTY.

03:09.923 --> 03:12.360
- YOU'VE BEEN PARTYING
EVER SINCE YOU GOT BACK.

03:12.393 --> 03:14.695
- SO WHAT IF I HAVE?
I-I'M FREE NOW,

03:14.728 --> 03:17.698
I CAN STAY UP ALL NIGHT AND
FUCK MY BRAINS OUT LIKE YOU.

03:17.731 --> 03:18.732
- [chuckles]

03:18.766 --> 03:20.368
LET'S DANCE.

03:20.401 --> 03:22.403
- I DON'T WANT TO.
- IT'LL BE GOOD FOR YOU.

03:22.436 --> 03:24.004
IT'LL TAKE YOUR MIND
OFF THINGS.

03:24.037 --> 03:24.972
- I SAID I DON'T WANT TO.

03:25.005 --> 03:27.775
- WELL, YOU ALWAYS LIKED DANCING
WITH JUSTIN.

03:41.489 --> 03:42.923
[background chatter]

03:42.956 --> 03:45.393
- OKAY, BOYS,
WHAT'LL IT BE?

03:45.426 --> 03:48.529
JESUS CHRIST,
WHAT HAPPENED TO YOU?

03:48.562 --> 03:50.564
- I'M NOT QUITE SURE,
BUT WHATEVER IT WAS,

03:50.598 --> 03:52.733
MY HEAD FEELS LIKE
THE DANCE FLOOR AT BABYLON.

03:52.766 --> 03:54.368
- YEAH, WELL, THAT'S
WHAT YOU GET FOR STAYING OUT

03:54.402 --> 03:56.537
SUCKIN' AND FUCKIN'
TILL ALL HOURS. HUH?

03:56.570 --> 03:57.738
ON A SCHOOL NIGHT.

03:57.771 --> 03:59.507
- I'M NOT IN SCHOOL, MA.

03:59.540 --> 04:01.475
- YEAH, WELL,
MAYBE YOU SHOULD BE.

04:01.509 --> 04:02.843
YOU GOTTA A LOT
OF LEARNIN' TO DO.

04:02.876 --> 04:04.412
- BEFORE WE START
THE LECTURE,

04:04.445 --> 04:06.480
COULD I ORDER FIRST,
PLEASE?

04:06.514 --> 04:08.048
- I WANT YOU TO HEAR
WHAT I HAVE TO SAY

04:08.081 --> 04:11.619
ON AN EMPTY STOMACH
SO MAYBE YOU'LL DIGEST IT.

04:11.652 --> 04:17.491
GET OVER DAVID, GET A JOB,
AND GET ON WITH YOUR LIFE.

04:17.525 --> 04:18.959
NOW...

04:18.992 --> 04:20.694
WHAT'LL IT BE?

04:20.728 --> 04:23.631
- BACON AND EGGS.
EGGS OVER EASY.

04:23.664 --> 04:26.500
VERY, VERY, VERY,
VERY EASY.

04:26.534 --> 04:28.001
- MMM, MAKE IT TWO.
- THREE.

04:28.035 --> 04:29.970
- AND PLENTY OF BLACK COFFEE.

04:30.003 --> 04:31.639
- YOUR MOM'S RIGHT,
SWEETIE.

04:31.672 --> 04:33.541
FOR YOUR OWN DIGNITY,

04:33.574 --> 04:34.875
YOUR OWN SELF-WORTH,

04:34.908 --> 04:37.478
NOT TO MENTION YOUR HALF
OF THE RENT,

04:37.511 --> 04:38.579
YOU NEED TO GO BACK TO WORK.

04:38.612 --> 04:39.947
- DOING WHAT?

04:39.980 --> 04:41.915
- WELL,
THERE'S ALWAYS THE BIG Q.

04:41.949 --> 04:44.952
- HE DOESN'T WANT TO GO BACK
TO THE CRAP EMPORIUM.

04:44.985 --> 04:48.456
HE NEEDS TO TRY SOMETHING NEW.
SOMETHING DARING,

04:48.489 --> 04:49.457
SOMETHING FABULOUS.

04:49.490 --> 04:51.392
- NO...
FUCK FABULOUS.

04:51.425 --> 04:52.726
HE NEEDS
SOMETHING STEADY,

04:52.760 --> 04:55.596
SOMETHING PRACTICAL,
SOMETHING SECURE.

04:55.629 --> 04:57.064
- LIKE BEING AN ACCOUNTANT?

04:57.097 --> 04:58.666
- HE SHOULD ONLY
BE SO LUCKY.

04:58.699 --> 05:00.534
YEAH, I'VE GOT
A PENSION FUND,

05:00.568 --> 05:02.570
HEALTH PLAN, MOST IMPORTANTLY,
PEACE OF MIND.

05:02.603 --> 05:03.937
I GO TO SLEEP EVERY NIGHT

05:03.971 --> 05:05.873
KNOWING THAT IN,
UH, 31 YEARS

05:05.906 --> 05:08.409
WHEN I RETIRE
FROM WERTSHAFTER AND COMPANY,

05:08.442 --> 05:11.512
I CAN MOVE DOWN TO BOCA,
LIVE LIKE A KING.

05:11.545 --> 05:12.980
- OR QUEEN.

05:13.013 --> 05:15.649
- HOW WOULD LIKE YOUR TOAST,
YOUR MAJESTY?

05:15.683 --> 05:18.552
WITH STRAWBERRY JAM OR CAVIAR?
[laughs]

05:18.586 --> 05:20.654
- [groans]

05:20.688 --> 05:23.824
- "ATTACH PART 'J'
TO PART 'K'...

05:23.857 --> 05:26.794
USING A...GRATCHET"?

05:26.827 --> 05:29.363
[scoffing] WHAT THE FUCK
IS A GRATCHET?

05:29.397 --> 05:30.864
- BEATS ME.

05:30.898 --> 05:33.767
I'M SURE MEL WOULD KNOW.
SHE'S A WIZ WITH HARDWARE.

05:33.801 --> 05:35.869
- OH, I BET.

05:35.903 --> 05:37.838
I THINK WE SHOULD JUST HIRE
SOMEONE ELSE.

05:37.871 --> 05:40.140
- HEY! IT'S YOUR DUTY
AS A FATHER

05:40.173 --> 05:41.709
TO BUILD YOUR SON'S
FIRST SWING SET.

05:41.742 --> 05:45.379
NOW GET CRACKING--I WANT IT
READY FOR HIS BIRTHDAY.

05:45.413 --> 05:46.980
- I KNOW, IT SEEMS LIKE
ONLY YESTERDAY

05:47.014 --> 05:48.449
I WAS JACKING OFF
INTO THAT CUP.

05:48.482 --> 05:49.583
- [giggling]

05:49.617 --> 05:50.784
AND YOU AND MICHAEL
AND JUSTIN

05:50.818 --> 05:53.120
WERE TEARING INTO THE ROOM.

05:53.153 --> 05:55.456
YOU COULDN'T BELIEVE
YOU HAD A SON.

05:55.489 --> 05:57.024
[socket wrench cranking]

05:57.057 --> 05:59.126
TWO SONS.

06:03.464 --> 06:04.732
- WHY DON'T YOU
GIVE HIS MOTHER A CALL

06:04.765 --> 06:07.000
AND SEE HOW HE'S DOING?

06:07.034 --> 06:09.002
- SHE DOESN'T EVER WANT ME
TO SEE HIM AGAIN.

06:09.036 --> 06:11.672
- I KNOW, BUT MAYBE
IF YOU SPOKE TO HER--

06:11.705 --> 06:13.707
- NO, SHE'S RIGHT.

06:13.741 --> 06:15.443
IT'S BETTER THIS WAY.

06:19.647 --> 06:21.982
WAIT, WAIT.

06:22.015 --> 06:25.453
FUCK THIS.

06:25.486 --> 06:27.154
MAYBE I'LL HAVE IT DONE
IN TIME FOR YOUR WEDDING.

06:27.187 --> 06:29.189
- OHH, THERE WON'T
BE ANY WEDDING.

06:29.222 --> 06:30.991
HMM, MEL TURNED ME DOWN.

06:31.024 --> 06:33.093
[both chuckling]

06:33.126 --> 06:36.630
OH, IT'S NICE TO SEE YOU
LAUGHING, FINALLY, ASSHOLE.

06:36.664 --> 06:40.033
- YOU FINALLY PROPOSED
TO HER AND SHE BLEW YOU OFF?

06:40.067 --> 06:41.569
HOW COME?

06:41.602 --> 06:44.905
- OH, FOR REASONS I'M SURE
YOU'D APPRECIATE.

06:44.938 --> 06:47.641
"I DON'T THINK A MEANINGLESS,
HETEROSEXUAL RITUAL

06:47.675 --> 06:50.711
WOULD PROVE OUR LOVE, AND IT
WOULDN'T BE LEGAL ANYWAY."

06:50.744 --> 06:52.546
- HEY, CAN'T ARGUE
WITH THAT.

06:52.580 --> 06:55.015
- HEY, I WAS ON THE DEBATE TEAM.
I CAN ARGUE ANYTHING.

06:55.048 --> 06:57.951
- BUT I THINK, FOR ONCE,
I AGREE WITH MELANIE.

06:57.985 --> 07:00.921
FUCK WEDDINGS.

07:00.954 --> 07:02.923
FUCK RITUALS, AND...

07:02.956 --> 07:05.959
FUCK THIS SWING SET!
- [chuckles]

07:05.993 --> 07:07.461
- MIKE!

07:07.495 --> 07:09.196
IT'S SO GOOD TO SEE YOU.

07:09.229 --> 07:10.631
- YOU TOO, TRACE.

07:10.664 --> 07:12.199
- WHAT MADE YOU COME BACK?

07:12.232 --> 07:13.934
YOU WERE REALLY EXCITED
ABOUT GOING.

07:13.967 --> 07:15.803
- DAVID AND I BROKE UP.

07:15.836 --> 07:18.205
- OH...TSK.
I'M SORRY.

07:18.238 --> 07:20.541
- YEAH.

07:20.574 --> 07:22.676
SO I'M JUST KIND OF
PICKING UP WHERE I LEFT OFF.

07:22.710 --> 07:25.112
I THOUGHT I'D COME BY HERE
AND SEE IF MY OLD JOB IS...

07:25.145 --> 07:27.247
- WELL,
LOOK WHO'S HONORING US

07:27.280 --> 07:29.216
WITH HIS PRESENCE.
- HEY, ANDREW.

07:29.249 --> 07:31.519
- NEVER THOUGHT I'D SEE YOU
AGAIN, NOVOTNY.

07:31.552 --> 07:33.554
- MIKE'S MOVED BACK
TO PITTSBURGH.

07:33.587 --> 07:37.525
- NO KIDDING?
MUST'VE MISSED IT ON THE NEWS.

07:37.558 --> 07:40.160
AREN'T YOU SUPPOSED TO BE
RESTOCKING?

07:40.193 --> 07:41.995
- YES, SIR.

07:46.834 --> 07:50.003
- SO THINGS DIDN'T
WORK OUT, HUH?

07:50.037 --> 07:51.739
- WELL, I WOULDN'T...
I WOULDN'T SAY THAT.

07:51.772 --> 07:54.041
I MEAN, SOMETIMES YOU NEED
TO TRY NEW THINGS.

07:54.074 --> 07:56.610
DISCOVER WHAT'S RIGHT
FOR YOU, AND...

07:56.644 --> 07:58.045
WHERE YOU REALLY BELONG,
AND I DISCOVERED

07:58.078 --> 08:01.649
THAT WHAT'S RIGHT
FOR ME IS...

08:01.682 --> 08:02.916
BEING HERE, YOU KNOW.

08:02.950 --> 08:05.118
MAYBE EVEN GETTING
MY OLD JOB BACK.

08:05.152 --> 08:07.120
- OHH, HATE TO BREAK
IT TO YOU,

08:07.154 --> 08:08.956
BUT YOUR OLD JOB'S
BEEN FILLED.

08:08.989 --> 08:10.658
- OH.
- AFTER YOU LEFT,

08:10.691 --> 08:11.892
DON PROMOTED ME.

08:11.925 --> 08:14.127
- THAT'S GREAT.
- YEAH.

08:14.161 --> 08:16.997
I WAS GLAD TO SEE
HE FINALLY CAME TO HIS SENSES.

08:17.030 --> 08:18.932
SO I GUESS
YOU'RE OUT OF LUCK.

08:18.966 --> 08:20.868
- I GUESS I AM.

08:20.901 --> 08:22.736
UM...

08:22.770 --> 08:25.873
WELL, IF YOU HAPPEN TO HEAR
OF ANYTHING...

08:25.906 --> 08:27.575
- WELL, AS A MATTER OF FACT,

08:27.608 --> 08:29.209
WE DO HAVE A POSITION
FOR WHICH I THINK

08:29.242 --> 08:30.744
YOU'D BE IDEALLY SUITED,

08:30.778 --> 08:32.680
SINCE YOU ALREADY HAD IT.

08:32.713 --> 08:35.949
ASSISTANT MANAGER.

08:35.983 --> 08:38.552
- YOU MEAN...
WORKING FOR YOU?

08:38.586 --> 08:41.922
- YOU GOT IT.

08:41.955 --> 08:45.025
LET ME KNOW
IF YOU'RE INTERESTED.

08:49.329 --> 08:51.699
- HE HAD NIGHTMARES
AGAIN LAST NIGHT.

08:51.732 --> 08:54.267
I WENT IN TO COMFORT HIM,
BUT, UH...

08:54.301 --> 08:57.638
THE DOCTOR SAYS IT'S...
NORMAL.

08:57.671 --> 08:59.773
[scoffs] IF YOU CAN
CALL THAT NORMAL,

08:59.807 --> 09:05.012
THAT KIND OF BEHAVIOR...
IF SOMEONE'S BEEN ATTACKED.

09:05.045 --> 09:06.614
BUT...
[sighs]

09:06.647 --> 09:08.882
TO SEE HIM IN
THAT KIND OF PAIN...

09:08.916 --> 09:10.851
YOU KNOW,
I WANT TO HELP HIM.

09:10.884 --> 09:13.854
ONLY THERE DOESN'T
SEEM TO BE ANY WAY.

09:13.887 --> 09:15.923
I CAN'T.

09:15.956 --> 09:18.058
- IT'S OKAY.

09:18.091 --> 09:20.193
[sniffles]

09:20.227 --> 09:21.194
- OH, HERE.

09:21.228 --> 09:22.796
- THANKS.

09:26.399 --> 09:27.901
- HAVE SOME COCONUT CAKE.

09:27.935 --> 09:29.903
- OH...NO, THANKS.

09:29.937 --> 09:31.772
- VIC MADE IT HIMSELF.

09:31.805 --> 09:34.074
- YEAH, IT'S MY WARM-UP
FOR GUS'S BIRTHDAY.

09:34.107 --> 09:35.208
- HE USED TO BE
A PASTRY CHEF.

09:35.242 --> 09:38.111
- BLACK BOTTOMS
WERE MY SPECIALTY.

09:38.145 --> 09:39.212
[clears throat]

09:39.246 --> 09:41.849
- I DIDN'T SAY A WORD.

09:46.286 --> 09:47.320
- MMM.

09:47.354 --> 09:49.957
THIS IS GOOD.
- TOO GOOD.

09:49.990 --> 09:51.859
- WE FAGGOTS
ARE A TALENTED BUNCH.

09:51.892 --> 09:53.093
YOU GOTTA HAND US THAT.

09:53.126 --> 09:55.729
- INDESTRUCTIBLE TOO.
[chuckling]

09:55.763 --> 09:58.198
IF AIDS AND GAY-BASHERS

09:58.231 --> 10:01.201
AND CRACKPOT CHRISTIANS
AND FUCKIN' REPUBLICANS

10:01.234 --> 10:06.406
CAN'T DESTROY YOU,
NOTHING CAN!

10:06.439 --> 10:08.842
- AND JUSTIN
WILL MAKE IT TOO.

10:08.876 --> 10:09.877
YOU'LL SEE.

10:14.347 --> 10:17.050
- AH. I GOTTA RUN.

10:17.084 --> 10:20.020
MOLLY'S GOING TO COME BACK
FROM HER PLAY DATE.

10:21.454 --> 10:24.091
THANKS FOR THE CAKE.
- [chuckles]

10:24.124 --> 10:26.193
WE'LL SEE YOU, JEN.

10:26.226 --> 10:28.929
- YOU KNOW, JEN, THEY SAY
THAT A BOY'S BEST FRIEND,

10:28.962 --> 10:31.865
ESPECIALLY A GAY BOY,
IS HIS MOTHER.

10:31.899 --> 10:34.201
BUT THAT'S
NOT ALWAYS THE CASE.

10:34.234 --> 10:36.937
MAYBE WHAT HE NEEDS RIGHT
NOW IS SOMEBODY ELSE,

10:36.970 --> 10:39.339
SOMEBODY WHO COULD GET
CLOSE TO HIM.

10:39.372 --> 10:43.143
MORE IMPORTANT, SOMEONE THAT
HE WOULD LIKE TO BE CLOSE TO.

10:43.176 --> 10:44.712
- DEBBIE,

10:44.745 --> 10:47.748
I'M SORRY, BUT NOT
AFTER WHAT HAPPENED.

10:48.916 --> 10:51.885
- WELL...IT WAS
JUST A SUGGESTION.

10:51.919 --> 10:54.087
- BESIDES, I CAN LOOK
AFTER HIM MYSELF.

10:54.121 --> 10:57.390
- OF COURSE YOU CAN.

10:57.424 --> 10:58.692
- OKAY.

11:21.314 --> 11:23.083
- BRIAN!

11:26.319 --> 11:27.721
BRIAN!

11:31.992 --> 11:33.761
I'M GLAD IT'S YOU.

11:33.794 --> 11:36.063
- WHO ELSE WOULD IT BE?

11:36.096 --> 11:38.198
WHERE YOU GOING?

11:38.231 --> 11:40.367
- IN.
- DID I SAY YOU COULD?

11:40.400 --> 11:43.003
- DON'T GIVE ME ANY SHIT,
ALL RIGHT?

11:43.036 --> 11:44.872
I NEARLY FREAKED OUT FIVE TIMES
GETTING HERE.

11:44.905 --> 11:46.807
- WELL, YOU'RE GOING TO HAVE
TO NEARLY FREAK OUT

11:46.840 --> 11:49.009
FIVE MORE TIMES
GETTING HOME.

11:49.042 --> 11:51.344
- I WANT TO SEE YOU.
- WELL, YOU CAN'T, OKAY?

11:54.114 --> 11:55.783
- WHY NOT?

11:55.816 --> 11:57.517
ARE YOU FUCKING SOME GUY?

11:57.550 --> 12:00.187
- NONE OF YOUR FUCKING
BUSINESS.

12:01.889 --> 12:03.991
NOW GO AWAY.

12:09.529 --> 12:11.231
- BUT WHY?

12:12.900 --> 12:13.967
WHY?

12:14.001 --> 12:16.336
[background chatter,
phones ringing]

12:29.016 --> 12:30.984
- I CAN'T BELIEVE WHAT
THIS GUY CAN TAKE.

12:31.018 --> 12:32.853
NO WONDER THEY CALL HIM
"THE CHUNNEL."

12:32.886 --> 12:35.522
- ARE YOU ON MISTERFISTER.NET
AGAIN?

12:35.555 --> 12:37.157
- IT'S MY LATE-AFTERNOON
COFFEE BREAK.

12:37.190 --> 12:39.259
- AS OPPOSED TO YOUR
EARLY-AFTERNOON COFFEE BREAK,

12:39.292 --> 12:41.261
YOUR LATE-MORNING COFFEE
BREAK...

12:41.294 --> 12:42.462
- SOME GUYS
GET ALL THE BREAKS.

12:42.495 --> 12:44.264
- WHEN DO YOU EVER FIND
THE TIME TO WORK?

12:44.297 --> 12:46.533
- I MANAGE TO FIT IT IN.

12:46.566 --> 12:48.068
ACTUALLY, RIGHT NOW

12:48.101 --> 12:49.837
I SHOULD BE WORKING
ON THE MAGRUDER REPORT.

12:49.870 --> 12:51.538
WERTSHAFTER'S
EXPECTING IT AT...

12:51.571 --> 12:54.141
HOLY SHIT. HE'S PLAYING
"HIDE THE HYDRANT."

12:54.174 --> 12:57.010
- THE FIRE HYDRANT?

12:57.044 --> 12:58.511
- FUCK!

12:58.545 --> 12:59.579
SHIT.
- WHAT?

12:59.612 --> 13:01.014
WHAT?

13:01.048 --> 13:02.249
- I JUST SPILLED COFFEE
ON MY PANTS.

13:02.282 --> 13:03.583
- WATCH OUT FOR THE CREAM.

13:03.616 --> 13:06.353
- I-I GOTTA GET OFF.
- SURE YOU DIDN'T ALREADY?

13:07.587 --> 13:09.022
- OH.

13:09.056 --> 13:12.592
- FUCK!

13:12.625 --> 13:13.861
- SCHMIDT.

13:13.894 --> 13:15.996
[man in video moaning]

13:19.933 --> 13:22.269
- [stammering]
M-MR. WERTSHAFTER, I CAN--

13:22.302 --> 13:24.938
I CAN--I CAN EXPLAIN THIS.
I, UH, UH...

13:24.972 --> 13:27.040
[stammering]

13:27.074 --> 13:28.175
UH...
[man in video moaning]

13:28.208 --> 13:29.176
FUCK.

13:29.209 --> 13:30.577
- FUCK!

13:32.245 --> 13:33.413
FUCK!

13:35.048 --> 13:37.017
[grunts]

13:37.050 --> 13:38.451
- JUSTIN, MY GOD,
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

13:38.485 --> 13:40.253
STOP IT! STOP!

13:40.287 --> 13:41.421
- WHY IS JUSTIN
FREAKING OUT?

13:41.454 --> 13:43.323
- MOLLY, GO BACK TO YOUR ROOM.
GO ON!

13:43.356 --> 13:44.557
JUSTIN, PLEASE,

13:44.591 --> 13:45.893
STOP IT, PLEASE--
[gasps]

13:45.926 --> 13:47.327
- YOU TOLD HIM

13:47.360 --> 13:49.196
YOU DIDN'T WANT HIM TO SEE ME
ANYMORE, DIDN'T YOU?

13:49.229 --> 13:50.530
- IT WAS FOR YOUR OWN GOOD,
AND HE AGREED.

13:50.563 --> 13:52.265
- YOU HAD NO RIGHT!

13:52.299 --> 13:54.334
- JUSTIN, I-I...
I JUST WANT YOU SAFE,

13:54.367 --> 13:55.936
I WANT EVERYTHING TO BE
ALL RIGHT. OH!

13:55.969 --> 13:57.570
- [shrieks and grunts]

13:57.604 --> 13:58.605
- WELL, GUESS WHAT?

13:58.638 --> 14:00.207
IT IS TOO LATE!

14:00.240 --> 14:01.909
THINGS ARE NEVER GOING TO BE
ALL RIGHT.

14:01.942 --> 14:04.211
MY LIFE IS FUCKED!

14:04.244 --> 14:06.113
CHRIS HOBBS SAW TO THAT.

14:06.146 --> 14:08.348
HE SHOULD'VE FUCKING
KILLED ME!

14:08.381 --> 14:10.483
- [sobs]

14:10.517 --> 14:12.052
[clattering]

14:12.085 --> 14:13.086
- UHH!

14:13.120 --> 14:15.355
- [panting]

14:15.388 --> 14:18.025
- AND THEN, FUCKING WERTSHAFTER
GAVE ME THE SHAFT!

14:18.058 --> 14:19.392
CAN YOU BELIEVE IT?

14:19.426 --> 14:21.494
- I COULDN'T BELIEVE IT
THE FIRST 300 TIMES YOU TOLD ME.

14:21.528 --> 14:23.997
- I MEAN, HE FIRED ME.
ME, THE HARDEST WORKING,

14:24.031 --> 14:26.233
MOST DEVOTED EMPLOYEE
HE'S GOT, AND FOR WHAT?

14:26.266 --> 14:27.500
- WANKING TO THE WEB?

14:27.534 --> 14:29.202
- NO, NO, NO, NO, NO.
I WASN'T WANKING.

14:29.236 --> 14:31.371
I WAS WATCHING, SAME AS
EVERYBODY ELSE IN THAT OFFICE.

14:31.404 --> 14:33.006
THE ONLY DIFFERENCE:
I WASN'T WATCHING

14:33.040 --> 14:34.207
WHAT EVERYBODY ELSE WATCHES.

14:34.241 --> 14:36.009
- STRAIGHT SEX!
- YEAH.

14:36.043 --> 14:37.644
IT'S FINE TO SALIVATE

14:37.677 --> 14:40.313
OVER SOME BIMBO WITH BOOBS
THE SIZE OF FLOTATION DEVICES

14:40.347 --> 14:42.482
STUFFING A ZUCCHINI
UP HER TWAT.

14:42.515 --> 14:45.052
BUT GOD FORBID YOU SHOULD SEE
SOME GUY WITH PECS OF DEATH

14:45.085 --> 14:46.619
SQUATTING ON A ROAD TEEPEE.

14:46.653 --> 14:48.388
OH, THEN YOU'RE INSTANTLY
OUT ON YOUR ASS!

14:48.421 --> 14:50.090
- THAT'S DISCRIMINATION
IN THE WORKPLACE.

14:50.123 --> 14:51.558
- YOU'RE DAMNED RIGHT
IT IS.

14:51.591 --> 14:53.293
IF HE THINKS FOR A MINUTE THAT
I'M NOT GOING TO FIGHT BACK

14:53.326 --> 14:55.528
BECAUSE I'M TOO COWARDLY
TO REVEAL MY SEXUALITY,

14:55.562 --> 14:58.999
LIKE YOU--NO OFFENSE--
THEN HE IS MIGHTILY MISTAKEN.

14:59.032 --> 15:00.400
- DON'T WORRY, TED.

15:00.433 --> 15:01.534
WITH YOUR EDUCATION
AND EXPERIENCE,

15:01.568 --> 15:02.635
YOU'LL FIND ANOTHER JOB.

15:02.669 --> 15:03.636
- YEAH, I WOULDN'T
BE SO SURE.

15:03.670 --> 15:05.572
NOT AFTER THEY FIND OUT
THE REASON I WAS CANNED.

15:05.605 --> 15:07.407
CHRIST!
WHAT AM I GOING TO DO?

15:07.440 --> 15:08.508
- MAYBE THERE'S SOMETHING
IN HERE.

15:08.541 --> 15:11.011
- WHAT, IN THAT FAG RAG?
PLEASE.

15:11.044 --> 15:12.012
- WELL, I WAS THINKING

15:12.045 --> 15:13.680
OF LOOKING FOR A MOONLIGHTING
POSITION MYSELF,

15:13.713 --> 15:17.150
SOMETHING TO AUGMENT MY INCOME,
AND MY TUSH.

15:17.184 --> 15:18.418
WHOO, WHAT'S THIS?

15:18.451 --> 15:20.420
"EARN UP TO $100
AN HOUR."

15:20.453 --> 15:22.289
AN HOUR?
- DOING WHAT?

15:22.322 --> 15:23.656
- WHY DON'T WE
CALL AND FIND OUT?

15:23.690 --> 15:25.625
[phone dialing]

15:25.658 --> 15:28.661
HELLO, YES, I--I CAME
ACROSS YOUR AD IN OUT.

15:28.695 --> 15:30.030
- IT WOULDN'T BE
THE FIRST TIME.

15:30.063 --> 15:31.631
- SHH!

15:31.664 --> 15:34.301
IS IT TRUE YOU CAN EARN UP
TO $100 AN HOUR?

15:34.334 --> 15:36.036
REALLY?

15:36.069 --> 15:38.405
AND, UM, AND WHAT EXACTLY
DOES ONE HAVE TO DO?

15:38.438 --> 15:40.307
- VOLUNTEER FOR HIDEOUS
MEDICAL EXPERIMENTS?

15:40.340 --> 15:41.241
- [scoffs]

15:41.274 --> 15:43.676
- SERVE AS A LIVE TARGET
FOR THE MILITARY?

15:43.710 --> 15:45.712
- OH, THAT'S ALL?
OH.

15:45.745 --> 15:47.514
IT'S ONE OF THOSE DOMESTIC
SERVICES.

15:47.547 --> 15:49.182
WAITERS, PRIVATE PARTIES,
MAIDS.

15:49.216 --> 15:51.284
- THAT'S A LOT OF BUCKS
FOR LIGHT HOUSEKEEPING.

15:51.318 --> 15:52.219
- I COULD MAKE
MORE IN A COUPLE HOURS

15:52.252 --> 15:54.287
THAN I COULD MAKE
IN A WEEK AT THE BIG Q.

15:54.321 --> 15:55.722
WHAT ABOUT YOU?

15:55.755 --> 15:58.591
- I HAVE AN M.B.A.
FROM WHARTON.

15:58.625 --> 16:00.193
I DON'T DO WINDOWS.

16:00.227 --> 16:01.328
- I HAVE THREE SEMESTERS

16:01.361 --> 16:02.695
FROM ALLEGHENY
COMMUNITY COLLEGE.

16:02.729 --> 16:03.763
I'LL DO ANYTHING.

16:03.796 --> 16:06.466
- OH, THAT'S FABULOUS.
YES.

16:06.499 --> 16:07.767
ALL RIGHT, WELL THANK YOU!
MM-HMM.

16:07.800 --> 16:11.571
THEY HAVE OPENINGS
RIGHT NOW.

16:11.604 --> 16:14.207
WELL, BOYS...

16:14.241 --> 16:15.642
THINGS ARE LOOKING UP.

16:15.675 --> 16:18.678
[exhaling rhythmically]

16:30.290 --> 16:32.759
- DID YOU EVER SEE
CITIZEN KANE?

16:32.792 --> 16:34.694
- YEAH.

16:34.727 --> 16:36.663
ALL MY LIFE,
ALL I'VE EVER HEARD

16:36.696 --> 16:40.067
IS HOW IT'S THE GREATEST
FUCKIN' MOVIE EVER MADE.

16:40.100 --> 16:43.436
SO I FINALLY RENT IT.

16:43.470 --> 16:46.806
THE GUY WHO PLAYS
THE LEAD IS FAT...

16:46.839 --> 16:49.776
THE STORY
ABOUT SOME SLED SUCKS...

16:49.809 --> 16:51.778
AND IT'S IN BLACK AND WHITE.

16:51.811 --> 16:55.782
- MAYBE YOU WERE EXPECTING
TOO MUCH.

16:55.815 --> 16:59.252
- LIKE WITH YOU.

16:59.286 --> 17:00.287
ALL I'VE EVER HEARD

17:00.320 --> 17:04.491
IS HOW BRIAN KINNEY
IS THE GREATEST FUCK EVER.

17:04.524 --> 17:07.494
IF YOU ASK ME, YOU'RE BOTH
HIGHLY OVERRATED.

17:07.527 --> 17:09.496
- EVERYBODY'S A CRITIC.
- AHH.

17:16.669 --> 17:19.472
- NEXT TIME, MAYBE YOU SHOULD
RENT BUTTHOLE BOYS.

17:19.506 --> 17:21.308
I GAVE IT TWO THUMBS UP.

17:25.778 --> 17:27.480
- I-I CAME AT THE WRONG TIME.

17:27.514 --> 17:30.183
- YOU TWO HAVE A LOT
IN COMMON.

17:35.588 --> 17:36.756
- MAY I COME IN?

17:44.897 --> 17:47.434
